        "timestamp": "2019-07-23 23:07:19.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI think it is needed to invoke the script with 3 arguments: username, password, and host, as they may change from installation to installation.   For example, policydb will not be valid when working in a csit environment.",
        "patchset_number": 1
